race.comment: The well-related SHAKO (2) (half to G2 winner Arcaded) absolutely loves this track and trip with three wins and four seconds from just seven starts and has been racing with a lot of confidence this campaign. Gets some weight off with the 3kg claim and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. XPRESSO (4) hasn't been too far off them in harder contests of late and will be rock-hard fit for this. Respect from the Vandyke barn. SUPER DAISY (3) strips fitter second-up from the break and is another to get some weight off with the claim. Top-three prospects. ALLOUTATIME (7) is drawn favourably from the inside marble and is sure to give backers a sight.
